⛔ CRITICAL — KNOWN AI MISTAKES TO AVOID:

1. WRONG ROOT KEYS — The seed script reads exactly "album", "photos", "post".
   These will BREAK the seed:
   ❌ "ALBUM"        ✅ "album"
   ❌ "DUMMY_PHOTOS" ✅ "photos"
   ❌ "NEW_POST"     ✅ "post"

2. MARKDOWN URLS — Never wrap URLs in markdown link syntax. This breaks JSON parsing.
   
   ✅ !important this is CORRECT "https://jiotriplah.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/photos/kobe/kobe-1.jpg"

3. SAVE AS UTF-8 WITHOUT BOM — When copying the JSON output into a .json file,
   save it as UTF-8 (no BOM). BOM causes a parse error: "Unexpected token 锘?"
   In VS Code: bottom-right corner → click encoding → "Save with Encoding" → UTF-8.

4. DO NOT USE SMART QUOTES — Use only straight double quotes " in JSON.
   ❌ "title": "神戶…"   ✅ "title": "神戶…"

