HOW TO USE THIS OUTPUT
────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

1. Save the JSON output as:  scripts/album data/{city}.json
   Example: scripts/album data/porvoo.json

2. Upload your photos to S3 under the matching folder:
   s3://jiotriplah/photos/{city}/{city}-1.jpg, {city}-2.jpg, ...

3. Run the seed command:
   npm run seed:all

The seed script will automatically:
- Skip if the city already exists
- Insert all photos
- Create the album (citySet) with the first favorite as cover photo
- Set photoCount automatically from the number of photos inserted
- Create the blog post



